      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: ur a pan, yummy
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: EndDialogue.Array.size
      value: 6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: RightDialogue.Array.size
      value: 5
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: WrongDialogue.Array.size
      value: 4
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'EndDialogue.Array.data[0]'
      value: "Well, I helped you learn the ropes, so you\u2019re on your own now"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'EndDialogue.Array.data[1]'
      value: Oh, Before I forget
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'EndDialogue.Array.data[2]'
      value: All Potions and ingredients are thrown out at the end of the day
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'EndDialogue.Array.data[3]'
      value: We keep NOTHING after a day is done.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'EndDialogue.Array.data[4]'
      value: "Anyways, I don\u2019t get paid enough, or at all, to deal with you"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'EndDialogue.Array.data[5]'
      value: "And the Wizard isn\u2019t about to give me a raise anytime soon."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: waitingDialogue.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'RightDialogue.Array.data[0]'
      value: "Well\u2026 this is pleasantly surprising."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'RightDialogue.Array.data[1]'
      value: You did well, little Goblin, good job.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'RightDialogue.Array.data[2]'
      value: The Wizard did a good job of hiring you
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'RightDialogue.Array.data[3]'
      value: "Where\u2019d he find you, by the way? The streets?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'RightDialogue.Array.data[4]'
      value: (...)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'WrongDialogue.Array.data[0]'
      value: "If you\u2019re trying to poison me, you\u2019re doing a grand job."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'WrongDialogue.Array.data[1]'
      value: "We\u2019re lucky I\u2019m your coworker and not a patron"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'WrongDialogue.Array.data[2]'
      value: "But it\u2019s your first time making a potion, so I can\u2019t be too
        harsh on your potion-making skills yet"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'WrongDialogue.Array.data[3]'
      value: "Just don\u2019t repeat wrong drinks, or I\u2019ll have to give ya a
        harsh talking to"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5554720266687678705, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'waitingDialogue.Array.data[0]'
      value: Drag and drop your ingredients and giggle water into the cauldron to
        craft your potion.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9140236158355592166, guid: 19861924c4847a84595abe9a8786d638,
